# 🇺🇸 Zeniris — Tutorial

## Installation
curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Broly199372/Zeniris-Realease-/main/install.sh | bash
source ~/.bashrc

## Creating a project
zen_new my_game

Structure created:
my_game/
  main.zn
  propriet.zn
  assets/
  mods/

## propriet.zn
modname = My Game
version = 1.0.0
description = My first game
author = YourName

## Basic structure
Every file starts with Start and ends with End:
Start

End

## Variables
Start

Health = 100;
Speed = 5,5;
Active = true;

100;     → integer
5,5;     → decimal
true;    → boolean true
false;   → boolean false

## Classes
Start

Class Player

End

## Functions
Class Player

Function Jump

Player.Jumping = On

End

End

## States
Always On or Off:
Player.Alive = On
Player.Dead = Off

## Dependencies
Function Run
Dep Player on1

Player.Moving = On

End

on1 means the first dep state must be On.
on2 means the first two must be On. And so on.

## Events
Event PlayerHit

Player.Hurt = On

End

## Full example
Start

Health = 100;
Speed = 5,5;

Class Player

Function Init

Player.Alive = On

End

Function Run
Dep Player on1

Player.Moving = On

End

Function Die
Dep Player on2

Player.Alive = Off
Player.Dead = On

End

Event PlayerHit

Player.Hurt = On

End

End

## Compile
zen_build my_game/main.zn

## Run
zen_run my_game

## Diagnose errors
zeniris diag my_game/main.zn

## Export
zen_apk my_game
zen_desktop my_game
zen_desktop my_game --windows


